data.description: Wow! Total Quality Remodel! Park-Like Setting! Excellent Location: medical, shopping! Ground floor offers 3 spacious bedrooms, a sitting room w/2nd kitchen, sunroom, (think in-law suite). Main floor boasts beautifully updated kitchen, Primary Bath with shower room, soaking tub (gotta see this!); enormous living area (can be living/dining) wall of windows w/sliders to upper deck, hard-wood paneled dining/office, laundry, and master suite w/sliders open to balcony, gorgeous master bath. Double decks with ground access and a connecting spiral staircase. This 2/3-acre lot backs to 14-acres of untouched nature & boast fall/winter city views! Excellent for entertaining! Attached 2022/2023 updates.
